---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact Us | Pita Cigars"
description: "Get in touch with Pita Cigars: visit our Miami factory or send us a message."
ogImage: "/assets/images/hero.jpg"
nav: contact
---
<section class="section contact section--page-top" id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="container contact__grid">
        <div class="contact__info">
          <p class="eyebrow">Get in Touch</p>
          <h2 class="section-heading" id="contact-heading">Visit Our Factory</h2>
          <p class="contact__lede">
            Questions about our blends, wholesale pricing, or becoming a retailer?
            We would be glad to hear from you.
          </p>
          <ul class="contact__details" role="list">
            <li class="contact__detail">
              <span class="contact__label">Address</span>
              <a class="contact__value" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=1895+NW+21st+St%2C+Miami%2C+FL+33142" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1895 NW 21st St, Miami, FL 33142</a>
            </li>
            <li class="contact__detail">
              <span class="contact__label">Phone</span>
              <a class="contact__value" href="tel:+13055481212">(305) 548-1212</a>
            </li>
            <li class="contact__detail">
              <span class="contact__label">Email</span>
              <a class="contact__value" href="mailto:pitacigars@att.net">pitacigars@att.net</a>
            </li>
            <li class="contact__detail">
              <span class="contact__label">Hours</span>
              <span class="contact__value">Mon&ndash;Fri 9AM&ndash;5PM &middot; Sat &amp; Sun Closed</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" class="contact__social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="2.5" y="2.5" width="19" height="19" rx="5.5" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4.2" />
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.15" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
            </svg>
            Follow us on Instagram
          </a>
        </div>

        <form class="contact__form" action="#" method="post" novalidate aria-label="Contact form">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="contact-name" class="field__label">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" class="field__input" autocomplete="name" required aria-required="true" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="contact-email" class="field__label">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" class="field__input" autocomplete="email" required aria-required="true" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="contact-message" class="field__label">Message</label>
            <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" class="field__input field__input--textarea" rows="5" required aria-required="true"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary contact__submit">Send Message</button>
          <p class="contact__feedback" aria-live="polite"></p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
